milestones.description: Malla and Bhandari's 61-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 58 between Malla and Anil Sah
Aarif Sheikh and Rohit Paudel's 82-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 47 between Paras Khadka and Aarif Sheikh
Rajbanshi and Lamichhane's 17-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Bhandari and Lamichhane
Naveed has broken the record for most sixes (18) in ODIs for UAE, going past Rameez Shahzad's 17
Aarif Sheikh and Rohit Paudel's 82-run partnership is NEP's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 58 between Anil Sah and Malla
Karan KC has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for NEP, going past Basant Regmi's 2
Aarif Sheikh has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for NEP, going past Airee
